race.comment: CHIEF WITNESS (7) has a win and a second from four attempts over this track and trip and Harley sticks in the saddle following that last-start victory. Anticipating another strong run. NAVYONTHEHIGHWAY (10) goes well for rider Fenlon who has four wins and a placing from seven rides. Again gets the benefit of her 2kg claim and may make her presence felt. DEMON DARB (3) resumes here but has a solid first-up record and has revved up for this with two recent trials. Can run a race while fresh. SPACE TRACKER (6) next in line from the inside marble.
